{"tid":1666181,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(文宣方向)香港警察無視清真寺規定，嚴重侮辱宗教自由！","createTime":"2019-10-21T01:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T03:54:56.000Z","uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f514eca099b7928eb52d149c7bd41b75836ff4","tid":1666181,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:15:51.000Z","msg":"香港警察可以無視法律<br />\n仲可以無視清真寺教條 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vsYAneJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvsYAneJ.jpg&h=97bed4de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYp7XN4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYp7XN4.jpg&h=612565ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xUsaa75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxUsaa75.jpg&h=e3fb1879&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8bx8UN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8bx8UN.png&h=a8aca5e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b07da3ba0dc7d94fefa71afc2f100517e950ff97","tid":1666181,"uid":268123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:17:45.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"5cf09fd9d7e7c38d24c0c7d4376ef150f5dfa240","tid":1666181,"uid":219583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:18:29.000Z","msg":"你都ON9既 蒙左臉你仲點睇我做緊SHOW<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c644a34aed4e114a4efffc00e44fd45866eeceb7","tid":1666181,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:19:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a69a4f089fe717eb9e1f429fda50afa6ec8ee8b","tid":1666181,"uid":165136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:52:47.000Z","msg":"個非華裔下屬在場唔提下上司<br />\n係搏炒定跣個上司<br />\n睇到佢咁無理由唔講"},{"pid":"09461d4d037115db75193d8db32cd5c090a94099","tid":1666181,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:00:06.000Z","msg":"推上國際！"},{"pid":"88add46777ae99834b4a6cfbc15ae867d059ac38","tid":1666181,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a69a4f089fe717eb9e1f429fda50afa6ec8ee8b","tid":1666181,"uid":165136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:52:47.000Z","msg":"個非華裔下屬在場唔提下上司<br />\n係搏炒定跣個上司<br />\n睇到佢咁無理由唔講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:02:23.000Z","msg":"咪又係一啖砂糖一啖屎"},{"pid":"ca6a94683261e38b59a6cbd9cbbbc49d867686d9","tid":1666181,"uid":315604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A9E7YF6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA9E7YF6.jpg&h=0b5e5612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TbEzDF8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http